951
01:23:22,400 --> 01:23:28,360
so to speak, to recognize that. And I think 
that's not always that obvious to people.  

952
01:23:28,360 --> 01:23:31,960
The world does feel really polarized, 
but people definitely are willing to  

953
01:23:31,960 --> 01:23:38,720
cross partisan boundaries to get to accurate 
