954
01:23:38,720 --> 01:23:45,000
It feels like as we rely more and more on what we 
know and understand about the world is becoming  

955
01:23:45,000 --> 01:23:53,480
social media online and moving this quickly, it's 
like I'm so thankful this exists because otherwise  

956
01:23:53,480 --> 01:24:01,360
it'd just be, what do we trust anymore? This being 
out aligns with we need this thing to exist at the  

957
01:24:01,360 --> 01:24:09,000
same time. And it feels like at the same time 
there's also people I just don't trust. I think  

958
01:24:09,000 --> 01:24:13,160
people have shifted from I trust what I read to, 
okay, I shouldn't just believe everything I'm  

959
01:24:13,160 --> 01:24:20,200
reading. Is there anything there you're noticing 
