968
01:25:09,320 --> 01:25:14,440
really going on. So historically I think this 
was called media literacy, but basic idea of  

969
01:25:15,360 --> 01:25:20,800
can you understand the ways in which things 
can go wrong and try to cut them yourself.

970
01:25:21,360 --> 01:25:27,440
Another aspect I think we help with that is 
discovery of the Community Notes. I think often  

