before Community Notes you could have just 
been living in a little news filter bubble,  

972
01:25:32,080 --> 01:25:35,040
or maybe there were fact checks 
out there that you should have  

973
01:25:35,040 --> 01:25:40,880
been reading but you weren't discovering 
them. So the fact that the note applies,  

974
01:25:40,880 --> 01:25:46,360
it is directly attached to the post and 
visible by anyone who sees the post helps  

975
01:25:46,880 --> 01:25:51,960
cross those filter bubbles and can kind of... 
I think for some people it's the first time  

976
01:25:51,960 --> 01:25:59,640
