but we have so many quality mechanisms 
in the system that that wasn't an issue,  

1014
01:28:43,560 --> 01:28:48,640
so we could keep quality high 
while opening up for that honesty.

1015
01:28:48,640 --> 01:28:52,800
Another question, you touched on this a 
